{"tid":651717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港語學個Page其實都好多野爆","createTime":"2018-05-03T09:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T02:24:07.000Z","uid":63183,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3ddba40dc40d477a1b1e57ddb5ad0778d990b664","tid":651717,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"碌返舊圖，早喺2014年已經好多發現<br />\n<br />\n教育局都承認，「仍未有確實證據，證明以普通話學習中國語文的學生的一般中文能力會有所改善。其中兩項研究發現，以普通話學習的學生的中文能力，與以廣東話學習的學生並無分別，甚或表現更差。」<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/640626162660779/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fphotos%2Fa.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633%2F640626162660779%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=18707efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/640626162660779/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n教院02年普教中推廣文件，《用普通話教中文的問與答》嘅序：<br />\n「語言政策的決定，考慮的不純粹是語言因素。語言政策的決定，政治上和經濟上的考慮遠遠超過語言上的考慮。用普通話教中文的決定，是屬於語言政策的範圍，許多涉及這方面的問題，在這本小冊子裏都提供了看法，希望香港的老師、校長和其他關心香港教育的人士，能從中得益。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/643139529076109/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fphotos%2Fa.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633%2F643139529076109%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=63fce279\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/643139529076109/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n發現教局話廣東話唔係法定語言：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/645809768809085/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fphotos%2Fa.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633%2F645809768809085%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=cbb49df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/645809768809085/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n教育電視：「廣州話只不過係方言，方言又點可以用黎書寫啊」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/654006347989427/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fphotos%2Fa.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633%2F654006347989427%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=4639144e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/654006347989427/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n教育電視：有人要用粵語一統天下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/654523704604358/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fphotos%2Fa.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633%2F654523704604358%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=f8eab852\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/photos/a.636947586361970.1073741830.593704294019633/654523704604358/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n連登仔碌下港語學D圖就唔洗個個月都札醒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476d4f3a16ff08522a4f278ad6aed9740ebabce7","tid":651717,"uid":63183,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/175620_e23b8d190b370e64de9f0a